; DIMEInstallerCA.def
;
; Explicit export table so that x86 (__stdcall) decorated names
; (_FunctionName@N) are suppressed.  MSI's GetProcAddress looks for the
; bare undecorated name exactly as written in DllEntry="…".
;
; On x64 this file is a no-op (x64 has no per-function name decoration).
;
; Note: no LIBRARY directive — the output filenames are DIMEInstallerCA_x64.dll
; and DIMEInstallerCA_x86.dll; specifying LIBRARY would cause LNK4070.

EXPORTS
    CleanupBurnARPEarly
    CleanupBurnRegistration
    CleanupDimeDllBak
    ConfirmAndRemoveNsisInstall
    ConfirmDowngrade
    EarlyRenameForValidate
    MoveLockedDimeDll
    RollbackMoveLockedDimeDll
    UnregisterDimeDll
